Letters were combined considering the most prominent shape/
terminal / or the stroke from a letter and, standard
proportions and elements were compromised to build a legible
and aesthetically consistent letters.
Due to the hybrid nature of the typeface, the
baseline, ascender height and the descender height
had to developed into two different heights,bench

in both languages.
